data.description: WELCOME HOME to this wonderful 3 bedroom 2 bath water front home  located in Central Florida's Active 55+ Community ~ VIENNA SQUARE!  Nicely appointed home boasts over 1900 square feet of living in this spacious open floor plan. An ideal home for entertaining and enjoying friends and family with ease!  The rear of the home boasts fabulous 8 ft. sliding glass double pane doors in conjunction with the numerous large windows throughout this home beams with natural light and sunshine! No worries about your electric costs.. this owner thought of it all by adding SOLAR PANELS eliminating high cost electric bills!  Stepping out from the Great room through the sliding glass doors to enjoy this large roofed and screened veranda overlooking a beautiful glistening pond offering you privacy along with wonderful morning sunrises.  This one-owner home features 18x18 light-toned ceramic tile throughout the foyer, great room, formal dining, eat-in kitchen and continuing into your large open kitchen.  Kitchen features 42" cabinets, stainless steel appliances, double sink, brushed nickel faucets, tremendous storage for your every need.  Master bedroom located in the rear of the home offers plush fawn toned carpet, large walk in closet. tall vanity with cultured marble countertop contiguous large his/hers sinks. and nice walk in shower.  Friends visiting?  Featured at the front of this home are ( 2) wonderful  nice size guest bedrooms, detailed with blinds and plush carpeting, along with a nicely appointed guest bath and pocket door giving your guests the utmost in privacy while visiting.   This home is a MUST to see!  This will not last long!  Give me a call to schedule your appointment right away.
